{"tid":1506500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大膽講句 搵大粒荷里活明星梗係無人出聲 要搵應該搵呢幾位","createTime":"2019-08-25T22:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:26:11.000Z","uid":285559,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b58b8b6cea272ab7608051668bf663fd28f543fc","tid":1506500,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T22:30:22.000Z","msg":"你班友搵大粒荷里活明星 <br />\n個個第日都要靠中國戲路 <br />\n梗係無人敢出聲<br />\n識搵梗係搵班已經同中國反面嘅明星<br />\n<br />\n1. 莎朗史東 (Sharon Stone)<br />\n莎朗史東因為同達賴喇嘛係friend子 <br />\n已經一直係中國黑名單上<br />\n係四川大地震之後甚至話係支那嘅報應 <br />\n實在係走得好前<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sharonstone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsharonstone&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=9c0fefcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sharonstone</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sharonstone/?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsharonstone%2F%3Fhl%3Den&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=df04fb76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/sharonstone/?hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n2. Katy Perry <br />\n之前去台灣開演唱會<br />\n著咗件太陽花衫同披起青天白日旗<br />\n已經被小氣支那永久禁止踏足大陸 <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/katyperry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkatyperry&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=7ed70907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/katyperry</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/katyperry/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkatyperry%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=9e981762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/katyperry/</a><br />\n<br />\n3. Maroon 5<br />\n2015果時想去中國開演唱會<br />\n點知因為喺twitter祝達賴喇嘛生日快樂而被禁 <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/maroon5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmaroon5&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=5d202840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/maroon5</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/maroon5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmaroon5%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=b1839fc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/maroon5/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. Selena Gomez<br />\n2016年被影到會見達賴 <br />\n被禁踏足大陸<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/selenagomez/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fselenagomez%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=44065717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/selenagomez/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/selenagomez\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fselenagomez&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=d280cef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/selenagomez</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 波叔 (Sacha Baron Cohen)<br />\n之前奧斯卡玩金正日骨灰 激親共產黨 大家都應該記得啦<br />\n雖然冇話比中國正式禁制<br />\n但係佢係香港之友 識講兩句廣東話（自己google）<br />\n而家又取材趙式芝拍戲 可能都會肯出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SachaBaronCohen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSachaBaronCohen&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=2bd5be72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SachaBaronCohen</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sachabaroncohen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsachabaroncohen%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a1c6ede3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/sachabaroncohen/</a>"},{"pid":"2b316fcbc982d2851ef4ea8d00aad47bdb77cf0e","tid":1506500,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T22:37:43.000Z","msg":"波叔有支持<br />\n<br />\nGerard Butler都有"},{"pid":"cc4c59775b10ee81c77e8bbda09dabd04a29